# Git mailmap — canonicalize contributor names/emails across the repo.
# See: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap
#
# Format:
#   <canonical-name> <canonical-email> <old-name> <old-email>
#
# GitHub honors this file for display of commit history, contributor lists,
# and blame views. It is non-destructive — no history is rewritten; only the
# displayed identity is canonicalized.

